{"tid":2415419,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科學家提出無須負能量曲速引擎","createTime":"2021-02-20T08:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T22:41:20.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"05d2e70a38995c633e71f2fe6919db205bc84eef","tid":2415419,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2102.06824.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2102.06824.pdf&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbktToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=7ea58346\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2102.06824.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://appliedphysics.org/physical-warp-drives/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappliedphysics.org%2Fphysical-warp-drives%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbktToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=8891b68a\" target=\"_blank\">https://appliedphysics.org/physical-warp-drives/</a><br />\n<br />\n物理學家阿庫別瑞在看過星艦迷航記後提出一種星際旅行的方法:&quot;讓太空船前面的空間<br />\n收縮，太空船後面的空間擴張。太空船本身在空間中不移動，但空間移動時會帶著太空<br />\n船前進，這樣就能規避相對論的光速限制&quot;。這種方案又稱為阿庫別瑞曲速引擎，然而創<br />\n造此種曲速空間需要大量的負能量奇異物質(目前所有觀測中，只有卡西米爾效應暗示這<br />\n種物質可能存在)，因此該方案過去被認為不可能實現。<br />\n <br />\n最近應用物理先進推進力實驗室的Bobrick和Martire發表了無須負能量的曲速引擎模型<br />\n，相關論文通過了同行評審。他們基於古典相對論開發了一個通用曲速引擎時空模型，<br />\n該模型包含了所有既有的曲速引擎定義，可在沒有出現阿爾別瑞方案缺陷的情況下使用<br />\n新度規。<br />\n <br />\n他們提出了亞光速正能量球對稱曲速引擎的一般模型，此外還構建了滿足量子不等式的<br />\n超光速曲速引擎方案，這種優化版阿爾別瑞度規能將負能量需求降低兩個數量級。他們<br />\n引入一種曲速引擎時空，其空間容量和時間速率可以以可控方式選擇。他們證明了任何<br />\n曲速引擎都是&quot;物質以一定速度慣性運動&quot;的外殼。論文表明:原則上，人類可以在已知的<br />\n物理理論的基礎上建造出亞光速球對稱曲速驅動時空。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://moptt.tw/p/Gossiping.M.1613805488.A.966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoptt.tw%2Fp%2FGossiping.M.1613805488.A.966&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbktToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=5de8715a\" target=\"_blank\">https://moptt.tw/p/Gossiping.M.1613805488.A.966</a>"},{"pid":"9c202d7394f55f2622ce1f134b2e5f165a644520","tid":2415419,"uid":18963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"亞光速球 曲速<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3112f9c2a5170d5c3be39f4f7bfb1fb7eb5a6b69","tid":2415419,"uid":32586,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:16:07.000Z","msg":"好似好勁雖然唔知講乜"},{"pid":"42cedf6b40e28fdc40593949dd26ab8cea463cf9","tid":2415419,"uid":271545,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"負能量我有喎"},{"pid":"d58e47b0dc09054de4f8f0a21b50c9a28672bbb7","tid":2415419,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"練下三頭肌投亞光速球唔難"},{"pid":"1aad779176ba7db8318d682d490106cc794d8444","tid":2415419,"uid":48080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:20:22.000Z","msg":"唔知到我死果日會唔會見證到佢誕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc60f369b5c76b87cd98a1ec59d1b34efde0acb8","tid":2415419,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:33:59.000Z","msg":"雖然唔明佢講咩鳩，不過好似好勁咁"},{"pid":"5f2d5f5d9cd41ace7ffa364f7dfead46c8abf56f","tid":2415419,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:49:10.000Z","msg":"同永動機果類野有無關係"},{"pid":"82c665b2cf2219ab6fc41d4777bd45b7eda9c3f2","tid":2415419,"uid":223525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:52:04.000Z","msg":"隻隻字都明，加埋一齊就睇唔明"},{"pid":"ebc907cf2ade8850652da4ca775dab46e23d9bf1","tid":2415419,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:55:25.000Z","msg":"連負物質都未有就寫到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7791ae8716a4129ce8ef752454f14b